S.FORM: Clarence Brookins nalecuhan i American, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza. Clarence Brookins i 1968 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 9 ku uwac atu silsil 118, namapili' tu nu Philadelphia 76ers putiput. bulad demiad, 1946 a mihca, Clarence Brookins, miunduay. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
